I seem to remember 9/11 this entire country was <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">RED</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->-<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:white;">WHITE</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  and <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;">BLUE</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->.  We were a untied nation, fighting for our loved ones, those families who were wronged and the lives that were lost.<br>
